data.description: PURCHASE FROM THE ORIGINAL OWNERS! This residence has never been leased and is ready for your personal touch! Featuring four bedrooms and three bathrooms, including a second en-suite space that offers a retreat-like experience, providing residents with a sense of exclusivity and comfort. The home is filled with natural light, thanks to plenty of windows in this newer concrete block construction built in 2016. An open floor plan allows for flexible design and encourages better social interaction. The expansive covered back patio backs up to a preserve, ensuring unbeatable privacy. Modern touches like granite bathroom counters, recessed lighting and 9'4" ceilings enhance the overall feel. Beyond the well-thought-out interior design, the home is equipped with a whole-house Generac generator, ensuring an uninterrupted power supply and offering peace of mind during power outages. The generator is designed to keep all essential systems running smoothly, allowing residents to maintain their daily routines without disruption. Pest tubes and gutters in place. Live in a neighborhood you can take pride in – Highly desirable Tuscany Woods consists of 200 homes built by Mercedes Homes and KB Homes. It is very well-maintained, featuring sidewalks, a community pool, clubhouse, cabana, and playground for residents only. Only 15 minutes to the world-famous Daytona Beach, eight minutes to Advent Health Hospital, and nine minutes to Tanger Outlets. Schedule your showing today! Motivated seller!!
